Fix List<T> causing periodic EditorPlugin crashes
Commented on #64937 C# EditorPlugin crashes editor on C# solution rebuild
I have a hunch this may have to do with how Godot marshalls C# Lists. I've changes the List to a Godot.Collections.Array and that seems to fix things.
